## Auth Strategy

**Method:** Signed JWT (HS256, 7-day expiry) issued after GitHub OAuth callback.

```
GitHub OAuth в†’ GET /auth/callback в†’ issue JWT в†’ frontend stores in localStorage
All API routes (except /webhooks and /auth) в†’ validate Bearer JWT in auth_middleware.py
```

JWT payload: `{ sub: user_id, github_id, login, exp }`

JWT secret: `в‰Ґ256-bit random` stored in `JWT_SECRET` env var. Rotating the secret
invalidates all active sessions (acceptable for v1).

Webhook auth is **separate**: `X-Hub-Signature-256` HMAC-SHA256 validated in
`webhooks.py` before any processing. See `schema.mdc` for full flow.

